#Alt+F1弹出菜单
Key F1 A M Menu FunMenu

#一些窗口操作的热键
Key F5 A 4 Close
Key F6 A 4 Maximize
Key F7 A 4 Iconify
Key F8 A 4 Move
Key F9 A 4 Resize
Key F10 A 4 FuncOnTop
Key F11 A 4 FuncFullScreen

#桌面切换热键
Key 1 A 4 GotoPage 0 0
Key 2 A 4 GotoPage 0 1
Key 3 A 4 GotoPage 1 0
Key 4 A 4 GotoPage 1 1
Key 1 T CS MoveToPage 0 0
Key 2 T CS MoveToPage 0 1
Key 3 T CS MoveToPage 1 0
Key 4 T CS MoveToPage 1 1

#快捷键启动程序
Key x A 4 Exec LC_CTYPE=zh_CN.utf8 xterm
Key t A 4 Exec Terminal
Key e A 4 Exec Thunar
Key l A 4 Exec leafpad
Key g A 4 Exec gimp
Key s A 4 Exec smplayer
Key m A 4 Exec claws-mail
Key c A 4 Exec gucharmap
Key b A 4 Exec VirtualBox
Key v A 4 Exec xterm -e vim
Key Up A 4 Exec audacious -p
Key Down A 4 Exec audacious -s
Key Left A 4 Exec audacious -r
Key Right A 4 Exec audacious -f
Key f A 4 Exec ~/.mozilla/firefox-shm.sh
Key Print A A Exec $[FVWM_DIR]/screenshot.sh
Key F12 A N QuickTerminal

Key XF86AudioMute A A Exec exec amixer set Master toggle
Key XF86AudioLowerVolume A A Exec exec amixer set Master 10%-
Key XF86AudioRaiseVolume A A Exec exec amixer set Master 10%+

#鼠标按钮绑定
Mouse 3 R A Menu FunMenu
Mouse 1 R A Menu FunMenu

Mouse 1 2 A Close
Mouse 1 4 A Maximize
Mouse 1 6 A Iconify

